attribs.name: repeating_npctrait_-MSISt6u0hphZ52oaHQT_description
attribs.current: If the DjinNPC dies, its body disintegrates into a warm breeze, leaving behind only equipment the DjinNPC was wearing or carrying.

attribs.name: repeating_npctrait_-MSISzGMZ0YlA2bf63Lc_description
attribs.current: DjinNPC can use its action to polymorph into any humanoid form, or back into its true form. Its statistics are the same in each form. Any equipment it is wearing or carrying isn't transformed. It revers to its true form if it dies.

attribs.name: repeating_npctrait_-MSITHn9ZgxttVZJqCAl_description
attribs.current:
The DjinNPC's innate spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 14, +6 to hit with spell attacks). It can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:
At will: Friends, Prestidigitation, Minor Illusion, Charm Person

attribs.name: repeating_npcaction_-MSITyFvvR3ZqVHjNKG9_description
attribs.current: DjinNPC attempts to beguile a creature within 30 feet of him. The creature must be able to see and hear DjinNPC. The creature must make a DC 14 Charisma saving throw. On a failure, the creature is charmed and DjinNPC can verbally command the creature to use it's reaction to move up to it's movement speed and make a single melee attack. The creature remains charmed by DjinNPC's and DjinNPC can use this action on subsequent turns to command the creature again. The creature can make the Charisma saving throw again at the end of each of it's turns, breaking free of the charm on a succes.

attribs.name: repeating_npcreaction_-MSIUb3Jhf84LpAU9zya_description
attribs.current: When a creature within 30 feet of DjinNPC targets him with an attack, DjinNPC can show his winning smile, forcing the creature to make a DC 14 Charisma saving throw. On a failure, the creature is forced to chose another target for his attack. If no other targets are in range, the creature's attack is wasted.
